    "Name": "Dengier DG1-O 'Peralta'",
    "Details": "Amy Peralta's personal loadout of a captured Dengier, this one-of-a-kind machine reflects the fighting style of a pirate who survived by being unpredictable. An ER PPC and Thumper Cannon cover range while an Artemis IV-guided MML 5 adds flexible missile output. A Retractable Blade replaces the original Hatchet for a more concealable melee threat. No two engagements with this machine played out the same way.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Protected Actuators</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.07</color></b>",
